from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
from sklearn.preprocessing import MinMaxScaler
from sklearn.decomposition import PCA

# Menghapus kolom-kolom yang tidak relevan
columns_to_remove = ['Sumber_Energi_Penerangan' ]

# Mengambil data yang relevan
data_reduced = numerical_data_cleaned.drop(columns=columns_to_remove, errors='ignore')

# Standarisasi data
scaler = MinMaxScaler()
data_scaled = scaler.fit_transform(data_reduced)

# Reduksi dimensi dengan PCA (menggunakan 2 komponen utama)
pca = PCA(n_components=2)
data_pca = pca.fit_transform(data_scaled)

# Melakukan K-Means clustering dengan 3 cluster
kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=3, init='k-means++', max_iter=300, n_init=10, random_state=42)
cluster_labels = kmeans.fit_predict(data_pca)

# Menambahkan kolom cluster ke dataset
data_reduced['Cluster'] = cluster_labels

# Menampilkan hasil clustering
data_reduced.head()

# Menghitung matriks korelasi tanpa kolom 'Cluster'
correlation_matrix_no_cluster = data_reduced.drop(columns=['Cluster'], errors='ignore').corr()

# Membuat heatmap dari matriks korelasi tanpa kolom 'Cluster'
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))
sns.heatmap(correlation_matrix_no_cluster, annot=True, cmap='coolwarm', fmt='.2f', linewidths=0.5)
plt.title('Matriks Korelasi Tanpa Kolom Cluster')
plt.show()

import seaborn as sns

# Membuat boxplot untuk membandingkan distribusi variabel antar cluster

for i, column in enumerate(data_reduced.drop(columns=['Cluster']).columns, 1):
    plt.subplot(3, 4, i)
    sns.boxplot(x='Cluster', y=column, data=data_reduced)
    plt.title(f'Boxplot - {column}')
    plt.tight_layout()

plt.show()

import pandas as pd
import numpy as np # Import numpy for select_dtypes

# Menghitung rata-rata untuk setiap variabel dalam masing-masing klaster
# Select only numerical columns (excluding the 'Cluster' column itself)
numerical_columns_for_mean = data_reduced.select_dtypes(include=np.number).drop(columns=['Cluster'], errors='ignore').columns

# Perform groupby on the numerical columns and calculate the mean
cluster_centers_original = data_reduced.groupby('Cluster')[numerical_columns_for_mean].mean()

# Menampilkan Final Cluster Centers berdasarkan variabel asli dalam bentuk tabel
print("\nFinal Cluster Centers berdasarkan variabel asli:")
cluster_centers_original_df = pd.DataFrame(cluster_centers_original)
print(cluster_centers_original_df.to_string()) # Use to_string() for better display

# Jika ingin menambahkan statistik deskriptif dari masing-masing cluster
# Select only numerical columns for descriptive statistics (excluding 'Cluster')
numerical_columns_for_describe = data_reduced.select_dtypes(include=np.number).drop(columns=['Cluster'], errors='ignore').columns

# Perform groupby on the numerical columns and calculate descriptive statistics
cluster_centers_descriptive = data_reduced.groupby('Cluster')[numerical_columns_for_describe].describe()


# Menampilkan Deskriptif Statistik untuk setiap cluster dalam bentuk tabel
print("\nDeskriptif Statistik untuk setiap cluster:")
cluster_centers_descriptive_df = pd.DataFrame(cluster_centers_descriptive)
print(cluster_centers_descriptive_df)
